cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE 

The paper deals with using deep learning for image-based plant disease detection, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The use of deep learning models for this task also involves machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The authors also mention the use of publicly available datasets, which could fall under information retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the use of neural networks for classification could also fall under neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
